  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist full game now!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Tukoni is a point-and-click puzzle adventure, based on a series of award-winning books by the Ukrainian artist Oksana Bula. Play as Tukoni, the forest spirits, as you meet unique characters, solve captivating puzzles, craft new items, and explore a magical world filled with kindness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419860/extras/eeca8d914573b9d5e1ad92233826637c.poster.avif?t=1773492125\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419860/extras/eeca8d914573b9d5e1ad92233826637c.webm?t=1773492125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419860/extras/eeca8d914573b9d5e1ad92233826637c.mp4?t=1773492125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Explore the world</strong><br>Explore the beautiful world hand-drawn by the Ukrainian artist Oksana Bula, and meet the characters inhabiting it!<br><br><strong>Solve puzzles</strong><br>Solve puzzles to help the forest animals, and to continue your journey!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419860/extras/2cfd33e3e4cc504d82abec130f1abd28.poster.avif?t=1773492125\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419860/extras/2cfd33e3e4cc504d82abec130f1abd28.webm?t=1773492125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419860/extras/2cfd33e3e4cc504d82abec130f1abd28.mp4?t=1773492125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Traveller’s Notebook</strong><br>Your notebook is your guide into the world of Tukoni. Check it often to see what’s next, and to find the cards that reflect your accomplished tasks.<br><br><strong>Crafting</strong><br>Combine items in your inventory to create unique new items that will help you in your adventure!<br><br><strong>No reading</strong><br>All the dialogs in the game are visualized through neat animated bubbles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419860/extras/fd451055e13924621cdaf96dada0110a.poster.avif?t=1773492125\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419860/extras/fd451055e13924621cdaf96dada0110a.webm?t=1773492125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419860/extras/fd451055e13924621cdaf96dada0110a.mp4?t=1773492125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
